Cell.Text: That doesn't make much sense. Where is this woman? Who is she?

Cell.Text: [S] G|You want my opinion, I'd say do what she wants. Take her home, and see who else is in this castle.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ02IsranBranchTopic4: She's asking me to take her home, to some castle.

Cell.Text: That's right. I used to be a Vigilant, but we had a difference of opinion. | They didn't think Skyrim has a vampire problem, and I did. | Kind of fitting that the Vigilants would be wiped out by vampires.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ02IsranLore1Topic1: Tolan said you're a vampire hunter.

Cell.Text: I've spent years cleaning the place up and making repairs. You can be damn sure the vampires won't be burning this place down.
Good. I assume you took care of that little infestation. Did you figure out what they were looking for in there?

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ02IsranIntroA1: Yes, the place was crawling with vampires.

Cell.Text: Damn fool. I told him not to go. The Vigilants always had more bravery than sense. | Did you at least find out what the vampires were looking for in there?

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ02IsranIntroA2: Tolan was right. And he's dead. The vampires killed him.

Cell.Text: <<Shared>> Well I don't know what that means. But we need to find out. She must either have something the vampires want, or be someone important to them.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ02IsranIntroB1: I don't know who she is. She says she lives in a castle near Solitude.
DLC1VQ02IsranIntroB2: She didn't want to follow me here. But she wants me to take her home.

Cell.Text: That would fit with the rest of it... You did right to play along. We need to find out what this is all about.
